      "relations": null,
      "text": [
        " لَا بَأْسَ بِأَنْ تَطَّلِيَ قَبْلَ الْإِحْرَامِ بِخَمْسَةَ عَشَرَ يَوْماً ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "A number of our companions, from Ahmad, from Safwan, from Abu Saeed Al Mukary, from Abu Baseer, ",
          "(It has been narrated) from Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> having said: ‘There is no problem with shaving (unwanted hair) before wearing the <span class=\"iTxt\">Ihraam</span>, by fifteen days’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "4. A number of our people have narrated from Ahmad from Safwan from abu Sa‘id al-Mukariy from abu Basir who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, has said, ‘It is not harmful to apply (hair remover) fifteen days before Ihram.’” "
        ]
      }
    }
